        <p class="cod-parable-link-eyebrow">✦ A Parable on the Canon</p>
        <p class="cod-parable-link-title">The Adventures of Barney and Clyde</p>
        <p class="cod-parable-link-hint">
          <span>A story of two books, one Guide, and the source of authority</span>
          <span class="cod-parable-link-arrow">→</span>
        </p>
      </a>

      <div class="cod-end"><span class="cod-end-mark">◆</span></div>
    </div>
  </article>
